{"type": "article", "id": 15860, "title": "Wooden KOTLIC lamp", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-10T07:51:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122441hOxnbYQR6NBzkasZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自塞尔维亚的设计事务所 Presek Design Studio 设计的灯饰，灵感源于塞尔维亚的传统中架锅用的三角架，灯就吊在架子中间，构成了悬空而对称的美。细长的木架简洁优雅，类似于衣架，富有生活气息。它还有一款是用亚光处理的钢材做架子，也是相似的原理，更有金属感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143145cRXH2a6xeASGtwF8.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"775\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.29166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261431460jei9zx3vMQa6tc7.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"811\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143146MNi9JudLkbPhyjFZ.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"810\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.35\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261431479DAUOGMJokWyRLXl.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"937\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}